🌐 What is DNS?

DNS (Domain Name System) converts:
👉 example.com → 192.168.1.1 (IP address)

Think of it like:
📖 “Internet phonebook”

🔍 Important DNS Records (Must Know)
A Record → Domain → IPv4 address
AAAA Record → Domain → IPv6
MX Record → Mail servers
NS Record → Name servers
CNAME → Alias domain
TXT → Extra info (SPF, verification, etc.)

